### NAV / Collateral & Treasury page
**Reorder**
- [ ] Move Treasury **above** Collateral (Manager can't miss it)

**Portfolio composition**
- [ ] Add grouping for spot vs. derivatives (open question with Timo re: Haruko)

**Venue breakdown** (already answers "where are my assets" — extend to two more questions)
- [ ] Add expense/income per holding (income stream − cost per custody account)
- [ ] Add margin position vs. required margin, with colour coding as it approaches 100% (liquidation risk)

**Treasury (new "flows" piece)**
- [ ] Show upcoming net subscription/redemption vs. fund's USD/stables availability
- [ ] Net flow number at top, with +subscriptions and −redemptions as inputs underneath
- [ ] Show cash position as a multiple of avg daily withdrawals **and** multiple of max withdrawals in next notice period (rationale for lock-ups & notice periods)

**Collateral**
- [ ] Add fees per account + blended fee rate
- [ ] Add income per account + blended income rate
- [ ] Show net fee rate (+income −fee) for the collateral position

**P&L**
- [ ] Replace position line items with categories: Realised PnL / Unrealised PnL (line-item detail belongs on the PnL page, not here)

**Balance Sheet** (MVP fine as-is — noted for future)
